headline: Citi lifts Spotify to Buy as valuation, catalysts strengthen the bull case
summary: Investing.com -- Citi upgraded Spotify to Buy in a note Friday, arguing it now sees “lots of reasons to like” the music-streaming platform’s stock, including attractive valuation, beatable estimates, and a series of upcoming catalysts.

headline: Fintech: Why regulation may actually be good for digital assets
summary: Citi US Equity Strategist Drew Pettit comes on Market Domination to discuss some of the winners he's seeing in the fintech space and what regulation could mean for digital asset companies like Coinbase (COIN).To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
